'''Karl Kesel''' (born [[January 7]], [[1950s#1959|1959]]) is an artist who illustrated the [[Jedi Prince]] series of young reader novels.

Raised in [[Wikipedia:Victor (town), New York|Victor, New York]], Kesel read comic books as a child. He later decided that he wanted to become a cartoonist. He eventually worked for [[Wikipedia:DC Comics|DC Comics]] and [[Dark Horse Comics]].

